'''2018年亚洲场地自行车锦标赛'''是第38届[[亚洲自行车锦标赛|亚洲场地自行车锦标赛]]，于2018年2月16日至20日在马来西亚汝来进行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cycling-malaysia.com/2018/04/17/asian-track-championships-2018-in-all-its-glory/|title=Asian Track Championships 2018 In All Its Glory|work=Cycling Malaysia|date=2018-04-17|accessdate=2020-10-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190916174338/https://www.cycling-malaysia.com/2018/04/17/asian-track-championships-2018-in-all-its-glory/|archivedate=2019-09-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>，这是马来西亚第六次主办亚洲场地自行车锦标赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1061545/kuala-lumpur-set-to-stage-asian-track-cycling-championships|title=Kuala Lumpur set to stage Asian Track Cycling Championships|work=Inside the Games|date=2018-02-15|accessdate=2020-10-01|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20201001030905/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1061545/kuala-lumpur-set-to-stage-asian-track-cycling-championships|archivedate=2020-10-01}}</ref>。共有21个国家和地区的运动员参加此次比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=http://accasia.org/sites/default/files/General%20Information_0.pdf|title=General Information|work=Asian Cycling Confederation|accessdate=2020-10-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001030614/http://accasia.org/sites/default/files/General%20Information_0.pdf|archivedate=2020-10-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

